data.filter_data: Absent: An HrC score of <2 is indicative of the absence of cancer. Low likelihood of cancer: An HrC score between 2 and 6 suggests a low likelihood of cancer. Moderate likelihood of cancer: An HrC score between 6 and 10 suggests moderate risk of developing cancer. High likelihood of cancer: An HrC score of >10 is indicative of cancer presence.
